OL,6,FA killer who inflicted more than 100
OL,7,Finjuries on a woman in a "brutal"
OL,8,Fattack has been jailed for life for
OL,9,Fher murder.
OL,11,FLouisa Hall, aged 43, suffered at
OL,12,Fleast 117 separate injuries at the
OL,13,Fhands of Steven Francis in his flat in
OL,14,FOatland Court, Little London, Leeds,
OL,15,Fin October 2023.
OL,17,FFrancis was found guilty of murder
OL,18,Ffollowing a trial at Leeds Crown
OL,19,FCourt. He was also convicted of raping
OL,20,Fanother woman in 2016.
