OL,6,FOn Thursday the 59-year-old was
OL,7,Fsentenced to life imprisonment, with a
OL,8,Fminimum term of 28 years.
OL,10,FThe court heard how ambulance staff
OL,11,Ffound Miss Hall, who was a sex worker,
OL,12,Fnaked and unconscious on the living
OL,13,Froom floor on 25 October 2023.
OL,15,FFrancis, who had called the ambulance,
OL,16,Fwas arrested at the scene. He claimed
OL,17,Fhe did not know Miss Hall but had
OL,18,Fbumped into her in Leeds city centre
OL,19,Fthat day and that she had followed him
OL,20,Fto his flat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
