OL,6,FHe said he had found her lying
OL,7,Funconscious after going to see a
OL,8,Ffriend.
OL,10,FA post-mortem examination found more
OL,11,Fthan 117 blunt force injuries to Miss
OL,12,FHall's head, chest, stomach, legs and
OL,13,Farms, inflicted with an unknown
OL,14,Fweapon, as well as evidence she had
OL,15,Fbeen strangled.
OL,17,FFrancis's account unravelled after
OL,18,FCCTV showed him with Miss Hall before
OL,19,Fhe claimed to have met her.
