OL,6,FThe friend he claimed to have gone to
OL,7,Fvisit told officers he had not seen
OL,8,FFrancis for about 13 years.
OL,10,FAs part of the murder investigation,
OL,11,Fdetectives reinvestigated a rape
OL,12,Fallegation against Francis by a sex
OL,13,Fworker in 2016.
OL,15,FHe was subsequently charged with two
OL,16,Fcounts of rape, assault, robbery and
OL,17,Ffalse imprisonment.
