OL,6,FSenior investigating officer, Det Ch
OL,7,FInsp James Entwistle, described
OL,8,FFrancis as "a very dangerous
OL,9,Findividual who has deliberately preyed
OL,10,Fon vulnerable women".
OL,12,FHe added: "Louisa Hall was subjected
OL,13,Fto an appalling level of violence at
OL,14,Fthe hands of Steven Francis in what
OL,15,Fwas a brutal and sustained attack that
OL,16,Fcruelly ended her life."
OL,18,FIn a statement Miss Hall's family
OL,19,Fsaid: "We hope nobody has to go
OL,20,Fthrough the pain and heartache that
OL,21,FSteven Francis has put us through."
