OL,6,FThe victim of the rape in 2016 said
OL,7,Fthe jury's guilty verdict had allowed
OL,8,Fher to sleep for the first time
OL,9,F"without nightmares".
OL,11,F"I hope this judgement will allow
OL,12,Fother victims of these offences to
OL,13,Fcome forward and get their justice,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
